---

<aside class="identity-message-card" aria-label="Mensaje de identidad">
  <span class="shield-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/assets/polla-mundialera/sections/03_jugador/19-shield-secplan-blue-gold-star.webp" alt="" width="1254" height="1254" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
  </span>
  <div>
    <h2>TU IDENTIDAD. TU POLLA. TU LEGADO.</h2>
    <p>Elige bien, esta será tu identidad en la Polla Mundialera.</p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .identity-message-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(247, 247, 242, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.08);
  }

  .shield-placeholder {
    display: grid;
    width: 3.4rem;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    place-items: center;
  }

  .shield-placeholder img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 9px rgba(7, 23, 53, 0.2));
  }

  div {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  h2,
  p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(0.98rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 950;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  p {
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .identity-message-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .shield-placeholder {
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
